%^BOLD%^-=%^CYAN%^Water Domain%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

The water domain calls upon both the waters of the depths and the moisture in the air to rain down fury upon your opponents.

Clerics with the Water Domain gain the following benefits:
- Cold resistance equal to their cleric level.
- %^CYAN%^Ice Bolt%^RESET%^ as an innate spell.

The water domain contains the following spells:

Fog Cloud, Sleet Storm, Tidal Surge, Vortex, Seamantle

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Lysara, Seija

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^